your way of living  Your where of living  Your why of living What if suicide was simply the death of the identity   and the rebirth of a new person in the same body Align thyself with a larger goal  Interest thyself in new pursuits  Change thine language and thine scenery  Rebuild thyself anew Should I decide to go   it will be obtained via shotgun to the head  In advance  prepare a living and a regular will  Prepare your room to be sanitized of mess and memory  as it will likely be left untouched for awhile  Try to do a few world positive things before you head out  Volunteer  write a book  help someone  Make your mark before you make your exit Thoughts
